 We are at present conducting a five-year follow-up study of the same cohort of patients and controls and plan a ten-year follow-up as well.

 The follow-up studies focus on brain structure (MRI), brain function, information processing, and psychopathology.

 We will correlate changes in structure and function to treatment, but no interventions (pharmacological or otherwise) are planned.

